      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h3 id=\"HippieDragonShading-Shading\">Shading</h3><p>To make this asset look convincing, I was required to work with a lot of different materials but I did not have different geometries to assign these materials to. All the different materials needed to combine under a single master shader so I thought the best approach for this kind of an asset would be layer shading using &quot;PxrLayerMixer&quot; and &quot;PxrLayer&quot; nodes to separate these different properties and use masks for a smooth transition between materials.</p><p>I had separate shader control for different areas of the body like the Petals, Leaves, Feet, area around the Eyes, Belly, Neck, Antenna, Tongue, Mouth etc.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image16.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image16.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729002&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=377\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/656834683/image16.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729002&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"994\" data-width=\"1999\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657391763\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image16.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"656834683\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"dd62448e-d6c3-4fc5-8d81-d95c45b20f89\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image16.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729002&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=754 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image16.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729002&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=377 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image4.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729046&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=638\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/656834683/image4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729046&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1679\" data-width=\"1999\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657391770\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image4.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"656834683\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"948716c8-ec88-4664-8662-6da3a5c17387\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729046&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=1276 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729046&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=638 1x\"></span><h5 id=\"HippieDragonShading-Petals\">Petals</h5><p>The lookdev for petals was one of the more crucial materials because it had to look thin and also transmit light the way flower petals do. Initially I tried to achieve the look through SSS with the help of a mask.</p><p>However, I was not satisfied with these results as the petals started to look more like wax, and the bright backlit tint was missing. To overcome this, I thought of a different approach where I combined Transmission using the Glass parameter along with SSS. To gain extra control, I used PxrRemap and PxrColorCorrect nodes.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image6.jpg\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image6.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729085&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=624&amp;height=624\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/656834683/image6.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729085&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"624\" data-width=\"624\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657391776\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image6.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"656834683\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"a2580b3e-a0cc-4a93-9819-e9910872e5b1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image6.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729085&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1024&amp;height=1024 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image6.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729085&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=624&amp;height=624 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image3.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729115&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=348\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/656834683/image3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729115&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"557\" data-width=\"1214\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657391782\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image3.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"656834683\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"3989a4b3-5533-401b-ba3b-acc419aa2387\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729115&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=696 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729115&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=348 1x\"></span><h5 id=\"HippieDragonShading-Leaves\">Leaves</h5><p>The geometry of the leaves is slightly thicker than the Petals so unlike the material for the petals, I did not need to use the transmission to get the backlit look similar to the petal. This is the result I got just using the SSS parameter.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image18.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image18.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729145&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=214\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/656834683/image18.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729145&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"542\" data-width=\"898\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657391788\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image18.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"656834683\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"9e74aee4-fe27-44bb-9581-5ddc6a978bc6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image18.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729145&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=712&amp;height=428 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image18.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729145&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=214 1x\"></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image22.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image22.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729174&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=214\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/656834683/image22.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729174&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"542\" data-width=\"898\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657391794\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image22.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"656834683\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"f177aa9e-ff1e-4fbd-84e0-611091b586dd\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image22.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729174&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=712&amp;height=428 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image22.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729174&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=214 1x\"></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h5 id=\"HippieDragonShading-Eyes\">Eyes</h5><p>I noticed in a lot of references that the eyes of frogs and some other reptiles have a metallic look. There are also gold foil-like flakes on some of them. I found it interesting and tried to achieve a similar look in Hippie’s eyes.</p><p>For the Iris and Sclera, I used both SSS and Specular Edge Color. For the metallic look, I increased the IOR slightly. This gave me that semi metallic look. Although the eye has that metallic shine but still it’s not really a true metal. In the end, it’s an organic material so instead of letting just the Specularity drive the color, I had combined it with subsurface to get some contribution from SSS as well.</p><p>For the golden flakes, I initially started off with just Specular Edge Color and cranked up the IOR to a much higher value to give it a pure metallic look. However, It would look almost black in the areas where little to no light hit. So ultimately, I stuck to the same approach as the rest of the eye but I kept the IOR higher that helped me get the shine similar to golden foil that I was going for.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image10.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729202&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=739\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/656834683/image10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729202&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1000\" data-width=\"1028\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657391800\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image10.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"656834683\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"0056ba2c-e900-4e30-8da8-6d169f5cb24d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729202&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1028&amp;height=1000 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/656834683/image10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592729202&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=739 1x\"></span><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"fullscreen-video-iframe conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"wide\" data-local-id=\"acb0df7d-3c87-44ed-a702-d1cb16bcc776\" data-macro-id=\"e2d6e81a-2158-4454-93c5-37dff79c3dad\" data-macro-name=\"widget\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"540\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/964899980\" style=\"border:none; margin:1em 0em;\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"960\">\n</iframe>\n\n<p /><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
